reviewText: Great DVD! Came in perfect condition. Very satisfied.
Watercolor painting instruction from Alvaro Castagnet, who is always passionate about his art and loves Havana, Cuba for its color and vivacity.

Alvaro is great fun as always and he is generous in demonstrating his methods. I've watched many how to watercolor DVD's and I like Alvaro's the best. All that said, good luck trying to copy this master. My friends who are not artists also enjoyed Alvaro and beautiful Havana with its old buildings and what we call classic cars.
